 Februari 18 , 1916 Friday 42 mls Stabl as usual Slept in this morn then after break tune overhaul my machin . In the afternoon I went out to Naglet-el-abid , the 2nd Regt HQs met our fellow then return home . The plane have been up sever time today state that the enemi are 50 mile closer today than they were yesterday was evid make for Bahnasa , one of our patrol came in touch of a 6 man pat of there , a camal detach was sent out to reconnaitr but no report has come to hand . Went up town tonight enjoy our stroll , found an up to date Draper there in the heart of all the nativ mud hut . Got home at 9.40 after supper turn in . Februari 19 , 1916 Saturday Stabl as usual The weather is still as good as ever. - I had anoth trip to Bahnasa , I rode down took my time , noth much happen on the way down I got there just in time for lunch set out again at 2.30 everyth went well until I was through Beni Mazar up at the Ktoul where after pass 4 buffalo one chase me I was in heavi sand at the time , I could n't get up enough speed to get away so I stop drew my gun as he charg I fire , the brute fell like a log , after that everyth went well , call in at Samalut got home at 6 readi for tea , went up the street at night then turn in at 10.30
